headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Seabreeze
content: The new Western Seabreeze is a private jet for the executive who needs to be flexible. Whether you’re landing on a desert runway or splashing down right next to your private yacht, this is business class for every occasion and locale. And if you’re the kind of high-earner who might have need of a machine gun and bomb bay, don’t worry, there’s plenty of room.
